>
<p>ChatGPT hit 5.7 billion monthly visits in January 2026. That number rivals Instagram and surpasses X (formerly Twitter) in total web traffic.</p>
<p>For anyone working in SEO, content marketing, or digital strategy, these ChatGPT traffic statistics shape how you plan, publish, and measure results.</p>
<p>We compiled 60 ChatGPT traffic statistics from sources including Similarweb, OpenAI, Statista, and Ahrefs. Every stat includes a source citation and year.</p>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>As of early 2026, ChatGPT receives approximately 5.7 billion visits per month.</strong> It ranks #6 globally across all websites and holds the #1 position in the AI chatbots category.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>Here is what the data covers:</p>
<ul>
<li>Monthly traffic and daily visit volume</li>
<li>Active user growth and milestones</li>
<li>Engagement metrics and query volume</li>
<li>Revenue, subscribers, and market share</li>
<li>How ChatGPT compares to Google Search</li>
<li>Mobile app downloads and demographics</li>
<li>Enterprise adoption and developer usage</li>
</ul>
<h2>General ChatGPT Traffic Statistics</h2>
<p><strong>1. ChatGPT recorded 5.723 billion total visits in January 2026.</strong>
Source: <a href="https://www.demandsage.com/chatgpt-statistics/">DemandSage</a>, 2026
That makes it one of the 10 most-visited websites on the planet, ahead of X and Wikipedia.</p>
<p><strong>2. February 2026 traffic dropped to 5.35 billion visits, a 6.5% month-over-month decline.</strong>
Source: <a href="https://www.demandsage.com/chatgpt-statistics/">DemandSage</a>, 2026
Seasonal dips are normal. January typically sees elevated usage after holiday downtime.</p>
<p><strong>3. ChatGPT peaked at 6.165 billion visits in October 2025.</strong>
Source: <a href="https://www.incremys.com/en/resources/blog/chatgpt-statistics">Incremys</a>, 2025
That represented a 4.43% increase over September 2025.</p>
<p><strong>4. September 2025 traffic reached 5.8 billion visits, up 7.6% month over month.</strong>
Source: <a href="https://www.superlines.io/articles/chatgpt-statistics/">Superlines</a>, 2025
Growth accelerated after the launch of new model capabilities.</p>
<p><strong>5. ChatGPT averages 193.33 million visits per day as of February 2026.</strong>
Source: <a href="https://www.index.dev/blog/chatgpt-statistics">Index.dev</a>, 2026
That translates to roughly 8 million visits per hour.</p>
<p><strong>6. ChatGPT ranks #6 globally and #1 in the AI Chatbots category on Similarweb.</strong>
Source: <a href="https://www.similarweb.com/website/chatgpt.com/">Similarweb</a>, 2026
It sits behind Google, YouTube, Facebook, Instagram, and Reddit.</p>
<p><strong>7. ChatGPT rivals Instagram and surpasses X and Wikipedia in total web traffic.</strong>
Source: <a href="https://www.incremys.com/en/resources/blog/chatgpt-statistics">Incremys</a>, 2025
Two years ago, ChatGPT was not in the top 50. The growth rate is unprecedented.</p>
<h2>Active Users and Growth Milestones</h2>
<p><img loading="lazy" alt="ChatGPT user growth milestones from 1 million to 900 million weekly active users" src="/images/blog/chatgpt-user-growth-milestones.webp" /></p>
<p><strong>8. ChatGPT reached 900 million weekly active users in February 2026.</strong>
Source: <a href="https://www.demandsage.com/chatgpt-statistics/">DemandSage</a> / OpenAI, 2026
That is more than double the 400 million weekly active users reported in February 2025.</p>
<p><strong>9. Daily active users sit at approximately 210 million.</strong>
Source: <a href="https://www.demandsage.com/chatgpt-statistics/">DemandSage</a>, 2026
For comparison, <a href="/blog/google-search-statistics/">Google processes over 8.5 billion searches daily</a>.</p>
<p><strong>10. Roughly 10.8% of the global population actively uses ChatGPT.</strong>
Source: <a href="https://www.superlines.io/articles/chatgpt-statistics/">Superlines</a>, 2025
No other <a href="/glossary/generative-ai/">generative AI</a> product has reached this adoption rate.</p>
<p><strong>11. Monthly active users grew from 358 million (January 2025) to 810 million (November 2025).</strong>
Source: <a href="https://textero.io/research/chatgpt-users-statistics-2025">Textero</a>, 2025
That is a net gain of 452 million users in 10 months.</p>
<p><strong>12. ChatGPT reached 1 million users in 5 days after its November 2022 launch.</strong>
Source: <a href="https://www.demandsage.com/chatgpt-statistics/">DemandSage</a>, 2022
It remains the fastest consumer product to reach 1 million users in history.</p>
<p><strong>13. ChatGPT hit 100 million users in approximately 60 days.</strong>
Source: <a href="https://www.demandsage.com/chatgpt-statistics/">DemandSage</a>, 2023
TikTok took 9 months. Instagram took 2.5 years.</p>
