<h2>ChatGPT vs Google Search Statistics</h2>
<p><strong>29. ChatGPT processes approximately 12% of Google Search volume.</strong>
Source: <a href="https://ahrefs.com/blog/chatgpt-has-12-percent-of-googles-search-volume/">Ahrefs</a>, 2025
That is a massive number for a product that did not exist 4 years ago.</p>
<p><strong>30. Google sends 190 times more traffic to websites than ChatGPT.</strong>
Source: <a href="https://ahrefs.com/blog/chatgpt-has-12-percent-of-googles-search-volume/">Ahrefs</a>, 2025
ChatGPT processes many queries but keeps users inside its interface. Google still drives the vast majority of referral traffic.</p>
<p><strong>31. Google makes up approximately 40% of all traffic to websites. ChatGPT accounts for just 0.21%.</strong>
Source: <a href="https://ahrefs.com/blog/chatgpt-has-12-percent-of-googles-search-volume/">Ahrefs</a>, 2025
This is the critical distinction. Volume does not equal referral traffic. For a deeper look at this shift, read our <a href="/blog/ai-search-referral-traffic-stats/">AI search referral traffic data</a>.</p>
<p><strong>32. Google receives 83.9 billion global visits per month. That is 14 times ChatGPT traffic.</strong>
Source: <a href="https://momenticmarketing.com/blog/google-reach-chatgpt-click-throughs">Momentic</a>, 2025
Google remains dominant in raw reach. But the gap is narrowing.</p>
<p><strong>33. The average ChatGPT user clicks 1.4 external links per visit. Google users click 0.6 per visit.</strong>
Source: <a href="https://momenticmarketing.com/blog/google-reach-chatgpt-click-throughs">Momentic</a>, 2025
When ChatGPT does send traffic out, the click-through rate per user is higher than Google.</p>
<p><strong>34. 64% of all ChatGPT referrals land on just 120 domains.</strong>
Source: <a href="https://momenticmarketing.com/blog/google-reach-chatgpt-click-throughs">Momentic</a>, 2025
ChatGPT referral traffic is extremely concentrated. Wikipedia alone receives <a href="/blog/wikipedia-chatgpt-citations/">47.9% of ChatGPT citations</a>. Getting <a href="/blog/get-cited-ai-search/">cited by AI search engines</a> requires specific optimization.</p>
