<li><strong>$10 billion ARR</strong> makes ChatGPT one of the fastest SaaS products to reach this milestone.</li>
</ul>
<p>These numbers carry direct implications for <a href="/blog/seo-statistics/">SEO strategy</a>. As ChatGPT and other <a href="/blog/ai-search-changing-seo/">AI search engines change how people find information</a>, businesses need to think about <a href="/blog/track-ai-search-visibility/">AI search visibility</a> alongside traditional organic rankings. Understanding <a href="/blog/ai-search-referral-traffic-stats/">AI search referral traffic patterns</a> helps you allocate resources between <a href="/blog/organic-vs-ai-search-budget/">organic and AI search</a>.</p>
